      "date": "2013-09-14 14:33:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/da734052-1d45-11e3-9c78-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  No failures.",
